responses.content:
```yaml
leads:
  - headline: TestComplete plugin stores credentials insecurely
    analysis: |
      The plugin stores the password for the TestComplete service in plain text in the Jenkins global configuration file. This password is used to log in to the user account that will run the tests.
    cwe: CWE-522
    function_names:
      - prepareServiceCommandLine
    filenames:
      - src/main/java/com/smartbear/jenkins/plugins/testcomplete/TcTestBuilder.java
    classification: very promising
```
